| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `calibration.py` | Main script — exercises 7.4, 7.5, 7.6 |
| `sheet7_report.md` | Written answers — exercises 7.1–7.7 |
| `README.md` | This file |

---

## What the script produces

| Output file | Exercise | Contents |
|-------------|----------|---------|
| `7.4_reliability_diagrams.png` | 7.4 | Reliability diagram per model |
| `7.4_ece_table.txt` | 7.4 | ECE per model (uncalibrated) |
| `7.5_temperature_search.png` | 7.5 | Validation NLL vs T per model |
| `7.5_ece_before_after.txt` | 7.5 | Best T + ECE before/after per model |
| `7.6_cost_loss_table.txt` | 7.6 | 2×2 cost-loss table for pedestrian model |

