## Drive structure expected

```
MyDrive/MyDataset/
├── 2026/2026/
│   ├── sheet3.zip           ← contains sheet3/dataset.py
│   ├── train.zip
│   ├── validation.zip       ← needed for 7.5 temperature search
│   └── test.zip
└── sheet3_results/
    └── checkpoints/
        ├── pedestrian.pt
        ├── traffic_light.pt
        └── vehicle.pt
```

