### CELL 10 — Save outputs to Drive
```python
import shutil, os
save_to = '/content/drive/MyDrive/MyDataset/sheet7_results'
os.makedirs(save_to, exist_ok=True)
shutil.copytree('/content/outputs', f'{save_to}/outputs', dirs_exist_ok=True)
print(f" Saved to {save_to}/outputs")
```

